node.text:
⁣Wrapping up this month with an episode of In the Kitchen with Jenn & Ben ~ 🌯  We whip up 3 quick meals using my favorite wrap from @olemex_labanderita! ⠀
⠀
〰️ 𝗢𝗺𝗲𝗹𝗲𝘁𝘁𝗲 𝗪𝗿𝗮𝗽 〰️ ⠀
Ingredients⠀
Carrot ⠀
Onion⠀
Eggs ⠀
Salt & Pepper⠀
Ketchup ⠀
Olive Oil ⠀
Lettuce ⠀
XTreme Wellness Wrap⠀
⠀
① Prep your veggies by roughly chopping into chunky pieces and place into a food processor to be minced⠀
② In your vegetable mixture, add your eggs and salt and pepper and mix until incorporated⠀
③ In a medium-heated pan, grease your pan with olive oil & pour your egg mixture thinly on the pan. Cook for about 2-3 minutes on each side⠀
④ Remove the omelette from the heat and chop into strips⠀
⑤ In a pan, heat up your wrap to your liking⠀
⑥ Assemble your wrap by placing ketchup, lettuce and your omelette into the wrap ⠀
⠀
〰️ 𝗠𝗲𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗲𝗮𝗻 𝗪𝗿𝗮𝗽 〰️ ⠀
Ingredients⠀
Cucumber ⠀
Tomato ⠀
Red Onion⠀
Dill ⠀
Cream Cheese⠀
Lettuce ⠀
Feta Cheese⠀
Salt & Pepper⠀
XTreme Wellness Wrap⠀
⠀
① Prep your vegetables by slicing your vegetables and dill⠀
② On your wrap, generously spread your cream cheese, then start filling up your wrap⠀
③ Finish off the wrap with feta cheese, salt & pepper. Enjoy ~⠀
⠀
〰️ 𝗟𝗲𝗳𝘁𝗼𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘀 𝗪𝗿𝗮𝗽 〰️ ⠀
Ingredients⠀
Light Mayo ⠀
Mustard⠀
Red Onion ⠀
Lettuce⠀
Egg Salad Mashed Potato⠀
Salt & Pepper ⠀
XTreme Wellness Wrap⠀
⠀
① Start your wrap by spreading light mayo and drizzling on your mustard onto the wrap⠀
② In your wrap, fill up your wrap with your desired ingredients - lettuce, red onion, egg salad mashed potato⠀
③ Season with salt & pepper ⠀
⠀

node.text: You're a...👼🏻✨ I never expected a simple fact like this could emotionally unravel me, but I guess this is just a taste of what parenthood does to you. Thank you to everyone who dropped some love on our gender reveal video. We definitely feel it and our hearts are so full. ♥️

node.text: A strange pregnancy craving that sparked recently were school meals issued by the state. Idk man. I guess I was just craving highly processed cardboard tasting carbs 😂 So @bengunsuk went above and beyond and whipped up these stinking cute "school meals" for me. He even made the smiley potatoes from scratch!! You can watch him make it on his channel. ✨

node.text: My social life has intentionally taken a nose dive these days, but that's okay. I genuinely love being in my own company and then slipping into the sheets by 9PM. Prioritizing rest has never been more important! 🛌✨

node.text: My whole pregnancy so far has felt like one looong 8 month trip~ inward.🌀✨I’ve felt every emotion on the spectrum from crumbling fear to tear-inducing gratitude. The amount of emotional growth and introspection that happens during pregnancy is astounding! It’s been a beautiful reprioritization of everything in my life. #35weeks

node.text: Time is the most precious non-renewable resource and the plot twist is that we never know how much left of it we have. These days I've trying my best to stretch out my days as long as possible by slowing tf down and saying "no" to everything that isn't a "hell yes." ⏳✨

node.text:
After 3 years and 18 collections, @eggieshop is closing its doors — closing this chapter of my life and focusing on the new one that is about to begin very shortly!

I’m beyond thankful to everyone who has supported Eggie over the last 3 years. It was always a pinch-me moment when I saw you guys in Eggie out on the streets. 

I want to say a massive thank you to everyone who was a part of the team. It really took a mf village to run this! We really did THAT! I will forever be grateful to each and every one of you. 

As a final goodbye, we are having a 70% off archive sale on http://eggie.us. Feel free to head on over and cop your fave pieces once and for all.
